<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>DESPRE CONCURS&nbsp;</strong></h3>
<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Primul&nbsp;Festival- Concurs&nbsp;Internațional&nbsp;de&nbsp;muzică&nbsp;instrumentală&nbsp; pentru&nbsp; copii&nbsp;<strong>,,Doremi&nbsp;Fest&rdquo;</strong>&nbsp; din Republica Moldova, orașul Chișinău este&nbsp;destinat&nbsp;tinerilor&nbsp;din &icirc;nvățăm&acirc;ntul&nbsp;muzical&nbsp;preuniversitar (secțiunea&nbsp; A- licee&nbsp;de&nbsp;muzică&nbsp;și&nbsp;secțiunea&nbsp;B- școli&nbsp;de&nbsp;artă)&nbsp;și&nbsp;se&nbsp;organizează&nbsp;pe&nbsp;clase&nbsp;de studii</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">(I-XII)&nbsp;și&nbsp;categorii&nbsp;de&nbsp;instrumente:&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
<ul style="margin-left: 30px;">
<li><strong>Pian</strong></li>
<li><strong>Vioară</strong></li>
<li><strong>Acordeon</strong></li>
<li><strong>Muzică&nbsp;de&nbsp;cameră&nbsp;(duo-sextet)</strong></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: justify;">____________________________&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"> &nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>JURIUL</strong>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Juriul&nbsp;va&nbsp;fi&nbsp; compus<span>&nbsp;</span>din cadre didactice&nbsp;universitare&nbsp;de&nbsp; specialitate&nbsp; din&nbsp;țară&nbsp;și&nbsp; din&nbsp; personalități&nbsp; ale&nbsp;lumii&nbsp;muzicale&nbsp; de&nbsp; peste&nbsp;hotare&nbsp; recunoscute&nbsp; la&nbsp; nivel&nbsp; internațional.&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">____________________________&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"> &nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>PREMII</strong>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Laureat&nbsp;I, II, III,&nbsp;Diplomant&nbsp;&nbsp;I, II, III&nbsp;pentru&nbsp;fiecare&nbsp;clasă&nbsp;și&nbsp;instrument.&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Diplome&nbsp;&nbsp;pentru&nbsp;toti&nbsp;profesori.&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"> &nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><em>Prima&nbsp; ediție&nbsp;a&nbsp; concursului&nbsp;se&nbsp; va&nbsp; desfășura&nbsp;&icirc;n&nbsp;perioada </em><strong> 25-27&nbsp;mai&nbsp;2018</strong><em>.</em>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">_____________________________&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"> &nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"> &nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>CONDIŢII DE PARTICIPARE</strong>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp; &nbsp;Concursul&nbsp;se&nbsp;va&nbsp;desfășura&nbsp;&icirc;ntre&nbsp;<strong>25-27&nbsp;mai&nbsp;2018</strong>.&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp; &Icirc;nscrierea&nbsp;la concurs se&nbsp;va&nbsp;face&nbsp;pe&nbsp;baza  <span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>formularelor&nbsp;de&nbsp;&icirc;nscriere&nbsp;online</strong></span>  aflate&nbsp;pe site-ul&nbsp;concursului.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Data&nbsp;limită&nbsp;pentru completarea&nbsp; ormularelor de&nbsp;&icirc; nscriere&nbsp; este&nbsp; 15&nbsp; mai&nbsp;2018.</strong>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Ordinea&nbsp; intrării&nbsp; &icirc;n&nbsp; concurs&nbsp; și&nbsp; programul&nbsp;de&nbsp; desfășurare&nbsp;vor&nbsp;fi&nbsp;afișate&nbsp;&icirc;n&nbsp;preziua concursului.&nbsp;</p>
