<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong><br /> </strong><strong>REGULAMENT</strong>&nbsp;</h2>
<p><strong><em>Tipuri de instrumente:&nbsp;PIAN, ACORDEON&nbsp;ȘI VIOARĂ</em></strong></p>
<p><strong><em>Secțiunea A &ndash;</em></strong><em>Licee de muzică - clasa I-XII</em>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong><em>Secțiunea&nbsp;B &ndash;</em></strong><em>&nbsp;Școli de arte -clasa I-VII&nbsp;</em>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong><em>GRUPURILE VOR FI FORMATE PECLASE</em></strong>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Pian:</strong>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>REPERTORIU</strong>:&nbsp;&nbsp; -o&nbsp;lucrare&nbsp; preclasică&nbsp; (polifonie)&nbsp; sau&nbsp; clasică&nbsp;(forma&nbsp;amplă)&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -o&nbsp; lucrare&nbsp; romantică&nbsp;,modernă&nbsp;&nbsp;sau&nbsp; romănească&nbsp;(la&nbsp;alegere)&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong><em>Secțiunea A-&nbsp;</em></strong><em>clasa I-IV-&nbsp;7 minute</em>&nbsp;</p>
<p><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -clasa V-VII-&nbsp;10&nbsp;minute</em>&nbsp;</p>
<p><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -clasa IX-XII-&nbsp;15&nbsp;minute</em>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong><em>Secțiunea B-&nbsp;</em></strong><em>clasa I-III-&nbsp;5&nbsp;minute</em>&nbsp;</p>
<p><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp;clasa&nbsp;V-VII-&nbsp;8&nbsp;minute</em>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Vioara,&nbsp;Acordeon:</strong>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>REPERTORIU</strong>:&nbsp; două&nbsp;lucrari&nbsp;diferite&nbsp;ca&nbsp;&nbsp; stil,&nbsp; formă&nbsp; şi&nbsp; caracter.&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong><em>Secțiunea A- </em></strong><em>clasa I-IV- 7 minute</em>&nbsp;</p>
<p><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -clasa V-VIII- 10 minute</em>&nbsp;</p>
<p><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -clasa IX-XII- 15 minute</em>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong><em>Secțiunea B- </em></strong><em>clasa I-III- 5 minute</em>&nbsp;</p>
<p><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - clasa&nbsp;IV-VII- 8 minute</em>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Muzica&nbsp;de camera (duo-sextet):</strong>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>REPERTORIU</strong>:&nbsp; două&nbsp; lucrari&nbsp; diferite&nbsp; ca&nbsp;&nbsp; stil,&nbsp; formă&nbsp; şi&nbsp; caracter.&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong><em>Secțiunea A-</em></strong><em> clasa I-IV- 7 minute</em>&nbsp;</p>
<p><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -clasa V-VII- 10 minute</em>&nbsp;</p>
<p><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -clasa IX-XII- 15 minute</em>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong><em>Secțiunea B- </em></strong><em>clasa I-III&nbsp;- 5 minute</em>&nbsp;</p>
<p><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </em><em>- clasa V-VII- 8 minute</em>&nbsp;</p>
